It&#39;s worked, but the best part is seeing the opponent&#39;s
face twist a little and ask, &quot;What?&quot;</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Cards</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Magi:<br>
